px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left-style: none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">13u50</strong></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left: 1px solid #eeeeee; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.3em;">Karting:<br />Na een korte briefing word je er op het racecircuit toegelaten. Gedurende de heat wordt er gestreden om de beste rondetijd neer te zetten. Na de race krijgen alle piloten een overzicht van de computergeregistreerde tijden en ronden.</p></td></tr><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left-style: none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">14u20</strong></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left: 1px solid #eeeeee; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.3em;">Verplaatsing naar het Outside Adventure Park (Westouterseweg 3, 8970 Poperinge)</p></td></tr><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left-style: none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">14u30</strong></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left: 1px solid #eeeeee; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse;">Miniquad:<br />De modder vliegt je om de oren en de fun kan niet meer op. Gas geven, remmen, door de bochten schuren en slippen, het hoort er allemaal bij! Dit alles maakt het rijden met miniquads een unieke en onvergetelijke ervaring.</td></tr><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left-style: none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">15u15</strong></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left: 1px solid #eeeeee; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.3em;">Quad:</p><p>Na dit spectaculaire opwarmertje gaan we over tot het zwaardere werk: quadrijdne met de Yamaha''s 350cc. Het uitdagende parcours zit vol avontuurlijke stroken en scherpe verraderlijke bochten. Recht blijven is de boodschap!&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left-style: none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: right;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">16u00</strong></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-left: 1px solid #eeeeee; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; border-collapse: collapse;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.3em;">Einde van de activiteiten</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0.5em; padding: 18px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #f96400; overflow: hidden; color: #f8d9d4; font-family: ''Open Sans'',Arial,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 